_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#features","content":"**On-demand loading**: Icons are loaded asynchronously from CDN only when needed"},"445":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-40","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#features","content":"**Automatic caching**: Once loaded, icons are cached for optimal performance"},"446":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-41","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#features","content":"**Flexible sizing**: Support for `width` and `height` props"},"447":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-42","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#features","content":"**Color inheritance**: Uses `currentColor` by default for seamless theme integration"},"448":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-43","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#features","content":"**Accessibility ready**: Built-in support for screen readers and keyboard navigation"},"449":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-44","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#features","content":"**TypeScript support**: Fully typed with comprehensive prop interfaces"},"450":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-45","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#features","content":"**Bento integration**: Extends Bento Icon with additional Antares-specific features"},"451":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-46","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#props","content":"The `Icon` component accepts the following props:"},"452":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-47","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#prop-inheritance","content":"The component extends `BentoIconProps` and passes through all standard HTML attributes and accessibility pr