docs/components/inline-drawer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/inline-drawer#aria","content":"For the sidebar rail, the toggle is your own control (e.g. a `ToggleButton`) — give icon-only buttons an `aria-label`, and the content stays in the DOM and accessible since nothing is hidden."},"562":{"id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer-31","page_id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/inline-drawer#best-practices","content":"Accordion → `Button slot=\"trigger\"` + `InlineDrawerPanel`. Sidebar rail → controlled state + always-visible children."},"563":{"id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer-32","page_id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/inline-drawer#best-practices","content":"For the rail, use numeric (px) `minSize`/`maxSize` so the width animates; `min-content`/`max-content` fit the content exactly but won't animate."},"564":{"id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer-33","page_id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/inline-drawer#best-practices","content":"`placement` does not flip in RTL; the side is decided by document/flex order."},"565":{"id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer-34","page_id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/inline-drawer#best-practices","content":"Don't nest InlineDrawers."},"566":{"id":"/docs/components/listbox","page_id":"/docs/components/listbox","type":"page","content":"ListBox","breadcrumbs":["Docs","Components"],"tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/listbox"},"567":{"id":"/docs/components/listbox-0","page_id":"/docs/components/listbox","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/listbox","content":"ListBox is a selectable collection of items rendered inline. Use it for non-popover pickers, inline lists, or as a building block for higher-level components like Select."},"568":{"id":"/docs/components/listbox-1","page_id":"/docs/components/listbox","type":"head