ied by the field wrapper (e.g. TextField, NumberField, Select). The group reflects them via data attributes on the group."],[1101,"The Tooltip component displays a description of an element on hover or focus."],[1120,"The tooltip uses `role=\"tooltip\"` and is associated with its focusable element via `aria-describedby`."],[639,"The tooltip uses `role=\"tooltip\"` and is associated with the info trigger via `aria-describedby`."],[266,"The whole field is a single focusable button; Enter/Space opens the popover"],[470,"These are re-exports of the underlying Bento Icon system methods. For complete API documentation, advanced usage patterns, and implementation details, see the `@bento/icon` and `@bento/svg-parser` package documentation."],[15,"This also works with autocomplete in IDEs and LLMs, so you can import from the root package and let your editor/agent suggest the available components."],[502,"This approach works well for SSR and small numbers of icons, but can lead to DOM bloat when the same icon appears many times."],[891,"Three sizes are available: `sm`, `md` (default), and `lg`."],[758,"Three track heights are available: `xs` (6px), `sm` (12px), and `md` (24px)."],[1400,"Tick labels on both axes with `xLabels` and `yLabels`."],[1401,"Tick marks (short lines) at each tick value. Controlled by `xTickMarks` and `yTickMarks`."],[1360,"Ticks"],[1416,"Time-series with date and currency formatting, gridlines, and nice Y-axis."],[783,"Timeline (past / current / future) derived from a single `currentStep` prop"],[1208,"Title displayed below the x-axis."],[1210,"Title displayed to the left of the y-axis."],[786,"Title truncation and RTL support"],[1358,"Titles"],[744,"To position a popover relative to a different element than its trigger, use the\n`triggerRef` and `isOpen` props instead of `<PopoverTrigger>`.\n`onOpenChange` is called when the user opens or closes the popover."],[1113,"To position a tooltip relative to a different focusable element, use the\n`triggerRe